t and upcoming experiments\nfor CMB lensing power spectra $C_{6000<L<8000}^{\\phi\\phi}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 26 Feb 2023 16:52:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
