yG frameworks, and\ncomes with releases of the raw text that we believe foster emerging language\nmodels and GNN research projects. An early public version of IGB is available\nat https://github.com/IllinoisGraphBenchmark/IGB-Datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2023 05:21:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
