sed probability of far-tail\nevents of reversed heat transfer. The decomposition of the local Nusselt number\n$\\mathrm{Nu_{loc}}$ traces this effect back to the sign of the temperature\ndeviation $\\tilde{\\Theta}$, revealing asymmetries of the heating and cooling\nplate on the thermal variance of the generated thermal plumes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 27 Feb 2023 13:04:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
